    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20200802/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-08-02"><time>2020-08-02</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE FOOD &amp; DRINK</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>This ham from Ten­nessee in the United States is mar­vel­lous, with a deep, smoky flavour ac­com­pa­ny­ing its salty punch.</p>
    <p>The plat­ter comes with fluffy Amer­i­can bis­cuits, pick­led sweet pep­pers and mus­tard – all of which balance out the salt in the ham well.</p>

